Package Music

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Aggrupation
    Abstract class Aggrupation that group both Album and Playlist classes and that defines the common methods and attributes between the two classes.
    Album
    Class of Album that inherit from Aggrupation and that defines object of music type Album.
    AlbumTupla
    Specific tuple composed of an integer and an album.
    Library
    Class Library that implements the necessary methods to describe the structure of an object of type library.
    MediaPlayer
    This class implements the functionality of MediaPlayer.
    Playback
    Playback class describes like a calendar with the playbacks per day.
    Playlist
    Class of Playlist that inherit from Aggrupation and that defines object of music type Playlist.
    Report  
    Search
    This class implements the methods used to make a search in the library.
    SearchList
    This class implements the methods used for the list returned in the global search method in class search.
    SearchOptions
    Class that only contains a constructor for the options available for searching.
    Song
    This class describes the structure of an object of the music type Song.
    SongTupla
    Specific tuple composed of an integer and a song.
    Tupla
    Class that describes the functionality of a Tuple
    UserTupla
    Specific tuple composed of an integer and a user.
